<TI>Inter-organizational scientific collaborations and policy effects: an ego-network evolutionary perspective of the Chinese Academy of Sciences</TI>

<TIss>interorganiz|scientif|collabor||polici|effect||egonetwork|evolutionari|perspect|||chines|academi||scienc|</TIss>

<SO>SCIENTOMETRICS</SO>

<LA>English</LA>

<DT>Article</DT>

<KWs>Industry-University-Research Institute (IUR) scientific collaborations||Government policies| Collaboration network| Dynamic evolution| Chinese|Academy of Sciences| Ego-network analysis</KWs>

<KWss>industri univers research institut iur scientif collabor|govern polici|collabor network|dynam evolut|chine|academi scienc|ego network analysi|</KWss>

<DEs>UNIVERSITY-INDUSTRY COLLABORATION| RESEARCH-AND-DEVELOPMENT| PUBLIC RESEARCH ORGANIZATIONS| INNOVATION SYSTEM REFORM| SMALL-WORLD NETWORKS| ABSORPTIVE-CAPACITY| TRIPLE-HELIX| KNOWLEDGE TRANSFER| PREFERENTIAL ATTACHMENT| GOVERNMENT RELATIONS</DEs>

