<TI>Net Increase? Cross-Lingual Linking in the Blogosphere</TI>

<TIss>net|increas|crosslingu|link|||blogospher|</TIss>

<SO>JOURNAL OF COMPUTER-MEDIATED COMMUNICATION</SO>

<LA>English</LA>

