<TI>Relational effects on knowledge integration: the differential effects on search and transfer</TI>

<TIss>relat|effect||knowledg|integr||differenti|effect||search||transfer|</TIss>

<SO>KNOWLEDGE MANAGEMENT RESEARCH & PRACTICE</SO>

<LA>English</LA>

