<TI>Knowledge heterogeneity and social network analysis - Towards conceptual and measurement clarifications</TI>

<TIss>knowledg|heterogen||social|network|analysi||conceptu||measur|clarif|</TIss>

<SO>KNOWLEDGE MANAGEMENT RESEARCH & PRACTICE</SO>

<LA>English</LA>

